# ParisVII_ProjectAndroid
FlashCard

==========================================
Projet de Android 
  by FAN YiZhe (#21502157)
  && LI Xiang (#21512427)
==========================================
This is a card game to help us to study the knowledge of some subject. like foreign language or geography.

Fonctions:
Be able to download the game in the internet and install.
Be able to create a game , delete a game , add new card, modify card, delete card.
Be able to listen background music. (3 different music to choose)
Be able to remind us a game we have not played for a long time.
Be able to do some settings.
Be able to count down the time left when we are answering the question.
Be able to give a tag to each card to classic their level of difficulty.
